quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,“۞ Chiwerengero chayandikira kwa anthu pomwe iwo ali m’kusalabadira ndi M’kunyozera
  21,2,“Palibe pamene ukuwadzera ulaliki watsopano wochokera kwa Mbuye wawo koma amaumvetsera uku akuchita zachibwana
  21,3,"“Mitima yawo ikunyozera (osalabadira za kudza kwa Qiyâma). Ndipo akunenezana mobisa amene adzichitira zoipa; (akuuzana motere): “Kodi uyu (Muhammadiyu) ndi ndani, simunthu monga inu? Kodi mukuudzera ufiti pomwe mukuuona?”"
  21,4,"“(Mneneri Muhammad{s.a.w}) adati: “Mbuye wanga akudziwa zimene zikunenedwa kumwamba ndi pansi; ndipo Iye Ngwakumva; Ngodziwa"
  21,5,"“Koma (osakhulupirira) adati: “(Izi zimene akufotokozazi) ndi maloto opanda pake.” (Ndipo nthawi zina amati:) “Koma zimenezi wazipeka.” (Penanso amati:) “Koma iyeyu ndi mlakatuli. Chonchotu, atibweretsere chizizwa monga mmene adatumiziridwa (aneneri) oyamba.”"
  21,6,"“Sadakhulupirire apatsogolo pawo, eni midzi imene tidaiononga (ngakhale kuti zozizwitsa adaziona); nanga iwo akhulupirira"
  21,7,"“Ndipo sitidawatume patsogolo pako, (iwe Mtumiki,) koma anthu, (osati angelo); tidawavumbulutsira (chivumbulutso Chathu.) Choncho, afunseni eni kudziwa ngati inu simukudziwa (nkhani zakale)"
  21,8,“Ndipo sitidawachite (aneneriwo) kukhala matupi osadya chakudya ndipo sadalinso okhala nthawi yaitali
  21,9,"“Kenako tidawatsimikizira lonjezo (la kuwathangata pa adani awo), ndipo tidawapulumutsa iwo ndi amene tidawafuna (mwa omwe adawatsata), ndipo olumpha malire (a Allah) Tidawaononga"
  21,10,“Ndithu tatumiza kwa inu buku lomwe m’kati mwake muli ulaliki wanu (malangizo kwa inu). Kodi simukuzindikira
  21,11,"“Ndi ambiri mwa eni midzi yomwe idali yosalungama, tidawaononga; ndipo pambuyo pake tidalenga anthu ena"
  21,12,"“Pamene adazindikira za chilango chathu, pompo adayamba kuchithawa"
  21,13,"“Musathawe, (kuthawa sikukupulumutsani), koma bwererani ku zimene mwasangalatsidwa nazo ndi m’malo mwanu, kuti mufunsidwe"
  21,14,"“Adanena: “Tsoka lathu ndithu! Tidali ochita zoipa.”"
  21,15,"“Kukuwa kwawoko sikudathe, kufikira tidawapanga ngati (mbewu) zokololedwa, mpaka kupuma kwawo kudazima (adafa)"
  21,16,"“Ndipo sitidalenge thambo ndi nthaka ndi zapakati pake, mwamasewera"
  21,17,"“Tikadafuna kupanga choti tiziseweretsa (sitidakapanga zomwe mukuzionazi) tikadapanga mwazomwe tili nazo, tikadakhala oti tichite (zachibwana)"
  21,18,"“Koma (chimene timachita ndi ichi), timachiponya choona pa chachabe ndi kuchiswa bongo bwake, ndipo chachabecho chimachoka. Ndipo chilango chili pa inu chifukwa cha zomwe mukunena (kumnamizira Allah)"
  21,19,"“Onse akumwamba ndi pansi, Ngake (Allah); ndipo amene ali kwa Iye (angelo), sadzitukumula pakumulambira, ndiponso satopa (ndi mapemphero)"
  21,20,"“Amamlemekeza usiku ndi usana, ndipo sagwidwa ndi ulesi"
  21,21,"“Kapena adzipangira milungu yochokera m’nthaka youkitsa akufa, (kotero kuti aichita kukhala milungu yawo mmalo mwa Allah)"
  21,22,"“Kukadakhala kuti ilipo m’menemo milungu ina (kuthambo ndi pansi) kupatula Allah, (ziwirizi) zikadawonongeka, wapatukana Allah Mbuye wa Arsh (Mpando Wachifumu) ndi zimene akunena (osakhulupirira)"
  21,23,"“Safunsidwa pa zimene akuchita, koma iwo adzafunsidwa"
  21,24,"“Kapena adzipangira milungu ina m’malo mwa Iye? Nena: ‘“Bweretsani umboni wanu (pa zimenezi), (izi ndikuuzani) ndichikumbutso kwa awa ali pamodzi ndi ine, ndiponso ndichikumbutso kwa amene adalipo patsogolo panga.” Koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa za choonadi, tero iwo akunyozera"
  21,25,"“Ndipo sitidatume patsogolo pako mtumiki aliyense koma tidali kumzindikiritsa kuti palibe mulungu wina wompembedza mwachoonadi, koma Ine; choncho ndilambireni"
  21,26,"“Ndipo (osakhulupirira) akuti: “(Allah) Wachifundo chambiri wadzipangira mwana.” Allah wapatukana (ndi zimenezo) koma (awa angelo) ndi akapolo (a Allah) amene alemekezedwa"
  21,27,"“Samutsogolera kuyankhula, ndipo iwo amachita molingana ndi malamulo Ake"
  21,28,"“(Allah) akudziwa zapatsogolo pawo (angelowo) ndi zapambuyo pawo, ndipo (angelowo) sangaombole (aliyense) koma yekhayo (Allah) wamuyanja, ndipo iwo, chifukwa chomuopa, amanjenjemera"
  21,29,"“Ndipo mwa iwo amene anganene kuti: “Ine ndi mulungu mmalo mwa Iye,” ndiye kuti timulipira Jahannam; umo ndi momwe timawalipirira ochita zoipa"
  21,30,"“Kodi osakhulupirira sadaone kuti thambo ndi nthaka zidali zophatikizana, ndipo tidazilekanitsa? Ndipo ndi madzi tidalenga chilichonse chamoyo. Kodi sakhulupirira"
  21,31,"“Ndipo tidaika mapiri panthaka molimbika kuti isagwedezeke ndi iwo, ndipo m’menemo tidaikamo misewu kuti alondole njira (ndikufika komwe afuna)"
  21,32,“Ndipo thambo tidalipanga monga tsindwi losungidwa (kuti lisagwe). Koma iwo akuzitembenukira kumbali zizindikiro zake
  21,33,"“Ndipo Iye ndi Yemwe adalenga usiku ndi usana, dzuwa ndi mwezi; chilichonse mwa izo chikusambira mozungulira m’njira mwake"
  21,34,"“Ife sitidawachite anthu amene adalipo patsogolo pako kukhala okhala nthawi yaitali. Nanga ukafa, kodi iwo adzakhala okhala nthawi yaitali"
  21,35,“Chamoyo chilichonse chidzalawa imfa; ndipo tikukuyesani mayeso ndi zinthu zoipa ndi zabwino. Ndipo nonsenu mudzabwerera kwa Ife
  21,36,"“Ndipo amene sadakhulupirire akakuona, akungokuchitira chipongwe. “Kodi ndi uyu yemwe akutchula milungu yanu (mwachipongwe)?” Pomwe iwo ndi amene akukana zakutchula (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri"
  21,37,“Munthu walengedwa ndi chikhalidwe chokonda zinthu (zake zonse) mwachangu. Posachedwapa ndikusonyezani zisonyezo Zanga; choncho musandifulumizitse (kukubweretserani chilango changa)
  21,38,"“Ndipo (osakhulupirira) akuti: “Kodi malonjezo awa adzakwaniritsidwa liti, ngati mukunena zoona?”"
  21,39,"“Chikhala kuti amene sadakhulupirire akudziwa chilango chimene chidzawapeza panthawi yomwe sangathe kutchinjiriza Moto kunkhope zawo ndi kumisana yawo ndipo kuti sadzathandizidwa, (sakadanena zimenezi)"
  21,40,“Koma (Qiyâma) idzawadzera mwadzidzidzi ndi kuwadzidzimutsa; kenako sadzatha kuibweza kapena kupatsidwa danga (kuti achite zomwe sadachite)
  21,41,"“Ndipo ndithu atumiki adachitidwa chipongwe patsogolo pako; choncho amene adachita chipongwe mwa iwo, zidawadzera zomwe adali kuzichita chipongwe"
  21,42,"“Nena: “Kodi ndani angakutetezeni usiku ndi usana ku masautso a (Allah) Wachifundo Chambiri?” Koma iwo akunyozera kukumbuka Mbuye wawo"
  21,43,“Kapena ali nayo milungu yowatchinjiriza m’malo mwa Ife? (Milunguyo) siingathe kudzithandiza yokha (nanga ndiye ingathe kuthandiza ena?) Ndipo (milungu) imeneyo siidzasamalidwa ndi Ife
  21,44,“Koma awa (osakhulupirira) tidawasangalatsa ndi makolo awo kufikira nthawi ya moyo wawo idatalika; kodi saona kuti tikulidzera dziko lawo ndikulichepetsa malire ake?. Nanga kodi iwo ndiwo opambana
  21,45,"“Nena: “Ndithu ndikukuchenjezani ndi chivumbulutso (cha Allah). Koma agonthi samva kuitana pamene akuchenjezedwa.”"
  21,46,"“Ndipo kukadawakhudza kumenya kumodzi kwa chilango cha Mbuye wako, ndithudi, (akadadzichepetsa nthawi yomweyo). Akadanena: “Tsoka kwa ife ndithu tidali osalungama.”"
  21,47,"“Ndipo tsiku la Qiyâma tidzaika masikero achilungamo, choncho mzimu uliwonse sudzachitidwa chinyengo pa chilichonse. Ngakhale (chinthucho) chili cholemera ngati njere ya mpiru, tidzachibweretsa; ndipo tikukwana (kukhala akatswiri) pa chiwerengero"
  21,48,"“Ndipo ndithu Mûsa ndi Harun tidawapatsa (buku) losiyanitsa pakati pa choonadi ndi chonama, ndiponso muuni ndi ulaliki kwa anthu oopa (Allah)"
  21,49,"“Omwe akumuopa Mbuye wawo ngakhale ali paokha, omwenso amaopa Qiyâma"
  21,50,“Ndipo iyi (Qur’an) ndi ulaliki wodalitsika umene tauvumbulutsa (kwa inu); kodi inu mukuikana
  21,51,"“Ndipo ndithu Ibrahim tidampatsa kulungama kwake kuyambira kale (kuubwana), ndipo tinkamudziwa (bwinobwino)"
  21,52,"“(Akumbutse anthu) pamene adauza bambo wake ndi anthu ake, “Nchiyani mafano awa omwe inu nthawi zonse mukupitiriza kuwapembedza.”"
  21,53,"“Adati: “Tidapeza makolo athu akuwapembedza. (Choncho nafenso Tikuwapembedza).”"
  21,54,"“(Iye) adati: “Ndithu inu ndi makolo anu mudali mkusokera koonekera.”"
  21,55,"“(Iwo) adati: “Kodi watibweretsera choonadi, kapena iwe ndi m’modzi mwa osereula?”"
  21,56,"“(Iye) adati: (“Iyayi, ine siwosereula), koma Mbuye wanu, ndi Mbuye wa thambo ndi nthaka amene adalenga zimenezi; ine pa zimenezi, ndine m’modzi wochitira umboni.”"
  21,57,"““Ndipo ndikulumbilira Allah, ndiwachitira chiwembu mafano anuwo pambuyo ponditembenukira misana kupita komwe mukupita.”"
  21,58,“Choncho adawaphwanya (mafanowo) zidutswazidutswa kupatula lalikulu lawo (sadaliswe) kuti iwo alibwelere (ndi kulifunsa zimene zachitika)
  21,59,"“(Iwo parnene adafika kumafano awo) adati: “Ndani wachita ichi pa milungu yathu? Ndithu iye ndi m’modzi wa ochita zoipa.”"
  21,60,"“Adati: “Tidamumva m’nyamata wina akuitchula (moipa); amatchedwa Ibrahim.”"
  21,61,"“Adati: “Mubweretseni pamaso pa anthu kuti amuone.”"
  21,62,"“Adati: “Kodi ndiwedi wachita ichi ku milungu yathu, E, iwe Ibrahim?”"
  21,63,"“(Iye) adati: “(Iyayi), koma wachita ichi ndi mkulu wawoyu. Choncho afunseni (kuti akuuzeni zenizeni) ngati amatha kuyankhula.”"
  21,64,"“Ndipo adadzitembenukira okha ndikunena kuti: “Ndithu inu ndinu oipa.”"
  21,65,"“Kenako adazyolitsa mitu yawo (ndikubwerera kuumbuli wawo) nanena kuti: “Ndithu iwe ukudziwa kuti izi siziyankhula (nchifukwa ninji ukutichita chipongwe)?”"
  21,66,"“(Iye) adati: “Kodi mukupembedza zomwe sizingakuthandizeni chilichonse, kusiya Allah, zomwenso sizingakupatseni masautso?”"
  21,67,““Kuyaluka nkwanu ndi zomwe mukuzipembedzazo kusiya Allah. Kodi simuganizira?”
  21,68,"“(Iwo) adati: “Mtentheni; ndipo pulumutsani milungu yanu, ngati inu mungathe kuchita zimenezi.”"
  21,69,"“Tidati: “E iwe Moto! Khala kuzizira ndiponso mtendere kwa Ibrahim.”"
  21,70,“Ndipo adamfunira chiwembu; koma tidawachita kukhala otaika zedi
  21,71,“Ndipo tidampulumutsa iye ndi Luti kupita ku dziko lomwe tidalidalitsa ku zolengedwa
  21,72,"“Ndipo (Ibrahim) tidampatsa Ishaq ndi kuonjezera Ya’qub, ndipo tidawachita onse kukhala abwino"
  21,73,"“Ndipo tidawasankha kukhala atsogoleri, owongolera mwa lamulo Lathu, ndipo tidawazindikiritsa kuchita zabwino ndi kupemphera Swala moyenera, ndi kupereka Zakaat; ndipo kwa Ife adali opembeza"
  21,74,"“Ndipo Luti tidampatsa luntha ndi kuzindikira, ndipo tidampulumutsa ku mudzi womwe anthu ake ankachita zoipa; ndithu iwo adali anthu oipa otuluka m’chilamulo (cha Allah)"
  21,75,“Ndipo tidamulowetsa mu chifundo Chathu; ndithu iye adali m’modzi wa ochita zabwino
  21,76,"“Ndipo (akumbutse za) Nuh, pamene adatiitana kale (kutipempha). Ndipo Ife tidamuyankha ndi kupulumutsa iye ndi anthu ake ku sautso Ialikulu"
  21,77,“Ndipo tidampulumutsa pa anthu amene adatsutsa Ayah Zathu; ndithu iwo adali anthu oipa. Ndipo onse tidawamiza (ndi chigumula chamadzi)
  21,78,"“Ndipo (akumbutse za) Daud ndi Sulaiman, pamene ankaweruza mlandu wa munda, pomwe mbuzi za anthu zidadya ndi kuonongaononga usiku mmenemo ndipo Ife tidali mboni pa kuweruza kwawo"
  21,79,“Tero tidamzindikiritsa za mlanduwo Sulaiman (kuposa tate wake Daud). Yense wa iwo tidampatsa kuweruza ndi kudziwa; ndipo tidagonjetsa mapiri ndi mbalame kuti zikhale pamodzi ndi Daud zikulemekeza (Allah); ndipo Ife ndi ochita chimene tafuna
  21,80,“Ndipo tidamphunzitsa (Daud) kapangidwe ka chovala chapankhondo chifukwa cha inu kuti chikutetezeni mkumenyana kwanu; kodi simungakhale othokoza
  21,81,“Nayenso Sulaiman tidamugonjetsera mphepo yamphamvu; inkayenda mwa lamulo lake kunka ku dziko lomwe talidalitsa (dziko la Sham); ndipo Ife pa chilichonse Ngodziwa
  21,82,"“Ndipo (tidamugonjetseranso) asatana omwe ankamubilira m’madzi (ndikumtolera ngale), ndipo ankachita ntchito zina kuonjezera pa zimenezi; ndipo Ife tidali owasunga (owateteza)"
  21,83,"“Ndipo akumbutsenso za Ayubu pamene adakuwira Mbuye wake (kuti): “Ndithu mavuto andikhudza, pomwe Inu ndi Achifundo kuposa achifundo!”"
  21,84,"“Choncho tidavomera (pempho lake); ndipo tidamchotsera mavuto omwe adali nawo, ndipo tidampatsa ana ake ofanana ndi omwe adali nawo kale ndikuonjezeranso ena onga iwo, (zonsezi monga) chifundo chochokera kwa Ife, (ndikuti zikhale) chikumbutso kwa ochita mapemphero"
  21,85,"“Ndipo (mutchule) Isimaila ndi Idrisa ndi Zul Kifli, onsewa adali mwa opirira"
  21,86,"“Tidawalowetsanso ku chifundo Chathu, ndithu iwo adali mwa anthu abwino"
  21,87,"“Ndipo (mtchulenso) Thun-Nun (Yunusu), pamene adachoka uku atakwiya, ndipo ankaganiza (kuti tamuloleza kusamuka) ndikuti sititha kumchita kanthu. Choncho adaitana mu mdima (mammimba mwa nsomba imene idamumeza, kuti): “Ndithu palibe mulungu wina wopembezedwa mwachoonadi koma Inu; mwayeretsedwa; ndithu ine ndidali m’modzi wa odzichitira zoipa.”"
  21,88,“Choncho tidavomereza (pempho lake) ndi kumpulumutsa ku madandaulo; umo ndi m’mene timawapulumutsira okhulupirira
  21,89,"“Ndipo (akumbutse za) Zakariya pamene adaitana Mbuye wake (kuti): “Mbuye wanga! Musandisiye ndekha; ndithu Inu ndinu wabwino kuposa alowa mmalo onse.”"
  21,90,"“Choncho tidamuvomera (pempho), ndikumpatsa Yahya ndikumkonzera mkazi wake. Ndithu iwo adali achangu pochita zabwino; ankatipempha mwakhumbo ndi mwamantha, ndipo adali odzichepetsa kwa Ife"
  21,91,"“Ndipo (atchulire za Mariya) yemwe adauteteza umaliseche wake (podzisunga); ndipo tidauzira mwa iye Mzimu Wathu, ndipo tidamchita iye ndi mwana wake kukhala chizizwa (cha Allah) kwa zolengedwa zonse"
  21,92,"“Ndithu uwu mpingo wanu, ndimpingo umodzi, ndipo Ine ndine Mbuye wanu; choncho ndipembedzeni"
  21,93,“Koma iwo adaswa chinthu chawochi pakati pawo (tero adakhala mipingo yosiyanasiyana). Onse adzabwerera kwa Ife
  21,94,"“Ndipo amene achite ntchito zabwino uku ali wokhulupirira, khama lake silidzakanidwa; ndithunso Ife tikumlembera zonse zimene akuchita"
  21,95,“Ndipo nkosatheka kwa eni mudzi umene tidauononga chifukwa cha machimo awo kuti asabwelere kwa Ife; (koma ndithu abwerera)
  21,96,"“Kufikira pamene Yaajuju ndi Maajuju adzatsekulilidwa (mpanda wawo), ndipo iwo adzakhala akuthamanga kuchokera m’phiri lililonse"
  21,97,"“Ndipo lonjezo la choonadi lidzafika; pamenepo maso a omwe sadakhulupirire, adzatong’oka uku akunena: “Tsoka pa ife! Ndithu tidali osalabadira (za chinthu) ichi; koma tidali oipa, (odzichitira tokha zoipa.)”"
  21,98,"“Ndithu inu ndi amene mukuwapembedza kusiya Allah, ndinu nkhuni za ku Jahannam. Ndipo inu (Jahannamyo) mudzalowa"
  21,99,"“Ngati awa akadakhala milungu yeniyeni, ndiye kuti sakadailowa, mmenemo onse adzakhala nthawi yaitali"
  21,100,“Mmenemo iwo adzakhala akubuula ndipo iwo mmenemo sadzamva (chifukwa makutu adzagontha)
  21,101,"“Ndithu amene ubwino wathu udawafika, iwo adzatalikitsidwa nawo (motowo)"
  21,102,"“Sadzamva mavume ake, ndipo iwo adzakhala nthawi yaitali m’zomwe ikukhumba mitima yawo"
  21,103,"“Kugwedezeka kwakukulu sikudzawadandaulitsa; ndipo angelo adzawalandira (ndikuwauza): “Ili ndi tsiku lanu lomwe mudali kulonjezedwa.”"
  21,104,"“(Kumbukirani) tsiku lomwe tidzakulunga thambo monga momwe amakulungira makalata okhala ndi malembo m’kati mwake; monga tidayamba kulenga zolengedwa poyamba, tidzabwerezanso (kuzilenga kachiwiri. Ndipo aliyense adzalipidwa pa zomwe adali kuchita) ili ndilonjezo lomwe lili pa Ife. Ndithu Ife ndi Ochita (zomwe tikunena)"
  21,105,"“Ndipo ndithu tidalemba m’zaburi (mu Masalimo buku la Daud) pambuyo polemba mu chikumbutso (Lauhil-Mahafudh) kuti: “Dziko (lapansi) adzalilowa akapolo Anga abwino.”"
  21,106,"“Ndithu pazimenezi (nkhani za aneneri), pali miyambo kwa anthu, opembedza (Allah)"
  21,107,“Ndipo sitidakutume koma kuti ukhale mtendere kwa zolengedwa zonse
  21,108,"“Nena: “Ndithu kukuvumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuti mulungu wanu ndi Mulungu Mmodzi; nanga inu mudzagonjera (zofuna Zake polowa m’Chisilamu)?”"
  21,109,"“Koma ngati anyozera, nena: “Ndalengeza (uthenga) kwa inu mofanana (popanda tsankho); sindidziwa kuti zomwe mukulonjezedwa zili pafupi kapena zili kutali.”"
  21,110,"““Ndithu Iye akudziwa mawu okweza, ndiponso akudziwa zomwe mukubisa.”"
  21,111,"““Ndipo sindikudziwa, mwina kuchedwetsa chilango chanu ndi mayeso akukuyesani ndikukusangalatsani ndi zokoma (za m’dziko) mpaka Idzakwane nthawi yoikidwayo.”"
  21,112,"“Adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Weruzani moona.” “Ndipo Mbuye wathu ndi (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri; Wopemphedwa chithandizo pa zimene mukusimbazo.”"